.DT
email
Discworld player help
email

.SH Name
.SI 5
email - set and show your email address.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
email <address>
.EI

.SH Describe
.SP 5 5
Email lets you set your email address so you can be contacted by the mud
administrators if for any reason they find it neccesary.  If you do not want
your email address seen by people other than lords or gods, just put : at the
front of it.  eg :fred@frog.frog.frog.edu
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
email frog@frog.edu
email :frog@frog.edu
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
finger, chfn
.EI
